Actions.Text: AMEND (T) AND RECOMMIT TO HIGHER EDUCATION

Title: Relates to dental laboratories
Summary: Relates to dental laboratories; defines terms; requires any dental laboratory operating, doing business, or intending to operate or do business in this state to register with the department of health; makes related provisions.
LawCode: Amd §§6611 & 6612, Ed L; add Art 5 Title 7 §§590 - 593, Pub Health L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law and the public health law, in relation to dental laboratories
